Not all Whole Foods are alike - this one is great!
I am so glad they built this just 5 minutes from my house because I don't care for the location on Tatum and Shea.
The wok bowl station rocks!
A great deal for $8!
Their orange chicken is delicious - their juice bar is great - the sandwiches they make are tasty.
